---
---

<section id="inicio" class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-hidden pt-20 bg-cream">


  <!-- Diagonal pattern (encima del overlay) -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="z-index: 2; background-image: url(\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='40' height='40' viewBox='0 0 40 40' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%239e6a28' fill-opacity='0.03'%3E%3Cpath d='M0 40L40 0H20L0 20M40 40V20L20 40'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E\");"></div>
  <!-- Radial glows -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="z-index: 2;">
    <div class="absolute top-1/3 right-0 w-md h-112 rounded-full" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(211,153,69,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-1/4 w-72 h-72 rounded-full" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(211,153,69,0.03) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 w-full pt-16 pb-10 lg:py-24 flex flex-col gap-8 lg:gap-10" style="z-index: 3;">

    <!-- Headline -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <h1 class="reveal font-serif" style="color: #210c04; font-size: clamp(52px, 7vw, 96px); line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.03em; font-weight: 900;">
        Orden,<br />Sin burocracia
      </h1>
      <div class="reveal" style="width: 48px; height: 3px; background: var(--accent);"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Subheading -->
    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <p class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold leading-snug" style="color: #210c04;">
        ¿Cansado de que el día a día no te deje liderar tu empresa?
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2 font-sans text-base lg:text-lg font-normal leading-loose" style="color: rgba(33,12,4,0.95);">Entrenamos a tu empresa para construir un sistema en el que puedas confiar: procesos simples, roles claros y expectativas concretas que se sostienen en el trabajo cotidiano.</p>

    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-3 font-sans text-base lg:text-lg font-normal leading-loose" style="color: rgba(33,12,4,0.95);">Así liberamos el tiempo de la dirección para que vuelva a enfocarse en lo que nadie más puede hacer: pensar el futuro de la empresa.</p>

    <!-- CTAs + Author card row -->
    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between gap-6 mt-8">

      <!-- CTAs -->
      <!-- Mobile CTA layout: top button full-width, bottom two side-by-side -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 w-full lg:hidden">
        <a
          href="https://calendly.com/nogoli"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn-shimmer w-full flex justify-center items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 font-sans text-sm font-medium tracking-wide transition-colors duration-300"
          style="background: #D39945; color: #240F07;"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="16" x2="16" y1="2" y2="6"/>
            <line x1="8" x2="8" y1="2" y2="6"/>
            <line x1="3" x2="21" y1="10" y2="10"/>
          </svg>
          Agendá tu charla de 20 minutos
        </a>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <a
            href="https://wa.me/5491130855891?text=Hola%20Sergio%2C%20te%20contacto%20desde%20tu%20web.%20Me%20gustar%C3%ADa%20agendar%20una%20charla%20para%20ver%20c%C3%B3mo%20pod%C3%A9s%20ayudarme%20a%20ordenar%20la%20operaci%C3%B3n%20de%20mi%20empresa."
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="flex-1 flex justify-center items-center gap-2 px-4 py-4 font-sans text-xs font-medium tracking-wide border transition-all duration-300 whitespace-nowrap" style="color: #210c04; border-color: rgba(33,12,4,0.40); min-height: 48px;" onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(33,12,4,0.06)'" onmouseout="this.style.background=''"
          >
            Hablemos
          </a>
          <a
            href="#metodo"
            class="flex-1 flex justify-center items-center gap-2 px-4 py-4 font-sans text-xs font-light tracking-wide border transition-all duration-300 whitespace-nowrap" style="color: #210c04; border-color: rgba(33,12,4,0.40); min-height: 48px;" onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(33,12,4,0.06)'" onmouseout="this.style.background=''"
          >
            Conocé el Método
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Desktop CTA layout: unchanged -->
      <div class="hidden lg:flex flex-wrap gap-4 items-center">
        <!-- TODO: replace Calendly URL with real link from client -->
        <a
          href="https://calendly.com/nogoli"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn-shimmer inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 font-sans text-sm font-medium tracking-wide transition-colors duration-300"
          style="background: #D39945; color: #240F07;"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="16" x2="16" y1="2" y2="6"/>
            <line x1="8" x2="8" y1="2" y2="6"/>
            <line x1="3" x2="21" y1="10" y2="10"/>
          </svg>
          Agendá tu charla de 20 minutos
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://wa.me/5491130855891?text=Hola%20Sergio%2C%20te%20contacto%20desde%20tu%20web.%20Me%20gustar%C3%ADa%20agendar%20una%20charla%20para%20ver%20c%C3%B3mo%20pod%C3%A9s%20ayudarme%20a%20ordenar%20la%20operaci%C3%B3n%20de%20mi%20empresa."
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 font-sans text-sm font-medium tracking-wide border transition-all duration-300" style="color: #210c04; border-color: rgba(33,12,4,0.40);" onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(33,12,4,0.06)'" onmouseout="this.style.background=''"
        >
          Hablemos
        </a>
        <a
          href="#metodo"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 font-sans text-sm font-light tracking-wide border transition-all duration-300" style="color: #210c04; border-color: rgba(33,12,4,0.40);" onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(33,12,4,0.06)'" onmouseout="this.style.background=''"
        >
          Conocé el Método
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Author card -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div>
          <p class="font-sans text-xs font-semibold" style="color: #210c04;">Sergio Martín Celuch</p>
          <p class="font-sans text-xs font-light" style="color: rgba(33,12,4,0.60);">Founder · Nogolí Consulting</p>
        </div>
        <div style="width: 144px; height: 144px; border-radius: 0; overflow: hidden; flex-shrink: 0;">
          <img
            src="/imagenes/perfil/sergio6.webp"
            alt="Sergio Martín Celuch"
            style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center 15%;"
            loading="eager"
            fetchpriority="high"
            decoding="async"
            width="144"
            height="144"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>


</section>
